videos.description: JJ Caldwell displays beautiful court vision finding Tyler Davis in the paint for the easy bucket.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Caldwell hits Davis with pretty pass

videos.description: DJ Hogg sinks the 3-pointer in rhythm for the Aggies in the first half.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Hogg drains 3-pointer

videos.description: Jordan Garnett flies through the paint and lays it in to tie it for the Norse in the second half.
videos.headline: Northern Kentucky's Garnett attacks the rim

videos.description: DJ Hogg launches a full-court inbound pass to Tyler Davis who throws it down for the Aggies.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Hogg throws full court outlet pass

videos.description: Will Johnson and Dr. John Thorton welcome Aggies freshman Savion Flagg to the broadcast to dive deeper into his first career double-double game.
videos.headline: Texas A&M wins a tight one against Northern Kentucky
